data.description: This turn-key Spanaway home is ready for its new owner! Coveted features like a secure gated entry, a three-car garage, community park, super-convenient location, and more await you at this abode! Set up with a wonderful floor plan, open-concept living, and tons of natural light, this home is perfect for any and all! You're sure to love its spacious rooms, Craftsman-style exterior, and fully-fenced backyard. Perfect for entertaining with many hosting spaces, and tons of parking! Only 15 mins from JBLM, shopping, and restaurants. What else are you waiting for? The Ridge at Southwood community is calling your name!
